name: BOTTOM FEEDERS\u2122 (Canceled)
blurb: Bottom Feeders is a simple addictive game where you plunge a net into the water, from a boat above, to catch cute little critters.

rewards.reward: We will give you special thanks for your contribution in a special Kickstarter section of our nobodinos website.

You will be invited to enroll in our Bottom Feeders public beta through Facebook. We will be hosting this beta around September 1st this year. It's coming up fast so jump on! Includes all previous rewards.

You will be invited to our community design forums so you can voice your opinion on the game. If you would like changes to be made, this is the place to voice them. One of our artists or designers will conduct occasional discussions or you can start one on your own. Includes all previous rewards.
FREE iPhone GAME! You will recieve a free copy of the paid version of Bottom Feeders for your iPhone. Includes all previous rewards.
FREE iPad GAME! You will recieve a free copy of the paid version of Bottom Feeders for your iPad. Includes all previous rewards.

A Bottom Feeders full color logo T-shirt. This t-shirt says \u201cI\u2019M A BOTTOM FEEDERS\u2026\u201d on the front \u2013 and \u201cBACKER!\u201d on the back of it with a Scrubber game character below it. Includes all previous rewards. (please donate an additional $10 for shipping if you live outside of the US)

BRONZE DEDICATION LEVEL - your name will be placed on the list as "Bronze Level Support" for our Zipper Interactive Dedication. A package of every title we shipped while Zipper was around will be donated by us to the Videogame History Museum. The VGHM and nobodinos will have a section of their website dedicated to each level of support. Includes all previous rewards.
You will recieve an O-Fish-al Bottom Feeders coffee cup in lime-green or underwater-blue. Includes all previous rewards. (please donate an additional $10 for shipping if you live outside of the US)

SILVER DEDICATION LEVEL - your name will be placed on the list as "Silver Level Support" for our Zipper Interactive Dedication. A package of every title we shipped while Zipper was around will be donated by us to the Videogame History Museum. The VGHM and nobodinos will have a section of their website dedicated to each level of support. Includes all previous rewards.

FREE iPhone CASE! You will recieve a special edition Bottom Feeders iPhone case with logo and game characters printed in full color. Includes all previous rewards. (please donate an additional $10 for shipping if you live outside of the US)

GOLD DEDICATION LEVEL - your name will be placed on the plaque as "GOLD Level Support" for our Zipper Interactive Dedication. Along with the package of Zipper titles we will have a plaque made with these names on it. The Videogame History Museum will hang this on a wall of the physical museum when it opens in dedication. Includes all previous rewards.

GOLD PLUS DEDICATION LEVEL - not only will your name appear on our Zipper dedication plaque, but you will become an official member of the Videogame History Museum for one year. This is an incredible honor and will allow you to attend any event sponsored by the museum including key note speeches and special exhibits held on and off site! This is valid on the date the physical museum opens. Includes all previous rewards.

RED SCRUBBER Level Backer - Work directly with the Art Director at nobodinos to come up with an awesome name for our bottom feeder catchin\u2019 trawlers. Whether it\u2019s \u201cBig Mike\u201d or with your son or daughters help\u2026 \u201cThe Stinker\u201d I know we can come up with a creative name together. There are only 4 boats in the first release, so only 4 of these pledge amounts exist\u2026 sorry! Includes all previous rewards.

BLUE SCRUBBER Level Backer. CAPTAIN OF THE SHIP! Work with our Art Director, Russ Phillips, to create a one-of-a-kind virtual cartoon character of yourself as Captain of the boat. Your character will be shipped as an available character for players to put on their boat, as well. Your name will be placed in the credits as an Artist with your work on this project. Artistic discretion and approval by team applies. Includes all previous rewards.

GOLDEN SCUBBER Level Backer. Russ Phillips, the Art Director of Bottom Feeders, will work with you directly to design a collectible character that will go in the game. This character will show up only when certain other items are collected as a major reward! You will also be listed as an \u201cArtist\u201d in the credits - tell all your friends that! Only two of these can exist in our game, along with the many other rewards we\u2019ve already designed so this is your chance. Includes all previous rewards.
